2008-08-06  Galen Wetterling  <wetterlg@wetterlg-laptop>

	* Sato/matchbox/theme-qvga.xml
	* Sato/matchbox/theme-vga.xml
	* Sato/matchbox/theme.xml
	* configure.ac
	
	Made a qvga-specific version of theme.xml, which is used in place 
	of the original theme.xml when --with-mode=qvga is passed as a
	configure option. The modified theme.xml file uses the qvga
	images.
	

